review.reviewBody:
The Best Pizza Experience Ever!🤩🤩
This take out is an absolute must-visit. Pizza was so fresh and a blend of crispy yet chewy crust, tangy tomato sauce, toppings and delightful cheeses. 😋🤤Would recommend it highly —the best pizza I have ever had, hands down. It’s my new cheat meal 🍕🍕
So good. Picky with pizza but this hits the spot
Pasty was tasty enough, but they forgot the addit topping I paid for and the cutl  .
Pizza was very tasty, and instructions followed, but the shrimp weren't fresh. They had started to turn.
